threads.title: 820-00850 5v, 0.16-0.20a
threads.message: Started another project and board not working, tested all cd chips and all same voltage. ppbus 12.32, but i noticed pp3v3_g3h not 3.3v, it showing 0.200mv. Where to start. board was liquid coffe damage. cleaned all spots and changed caps what was corroded.

threads.title: 820-00850 5v, 0.16-0.20a
threads.message:
You must check 3V3_G3H_RTC first.
Also check PMIC voltages, on its surrounding coils.

Did you try DFU?
